{"tid":1602230,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"工黨常委教育幹事何偉航 西貢遭4名白衣人持棍圍毆","createTime":"2019-09-29T10:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T10:38:12.000Z","uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"de3191c54b301660b25e45c1ca631b6c90e83271","tid":1602230,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:38:12.000Z","msg":"西貢發生傷人案，下午4時許，工黨常委兼職工盟工會教育幹事何偉航途經萬年街23號對開時，突遭4名白衣人持棍圍毆，附近一名女街坊阻止時亦被打傷，兇徒事後四散。警員接報到場，將何偉航及受傷女街坊一併送院治理。警方正在現場調查，追緝4名與案有關男子。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190929&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60098050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190929%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60098050&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=3036e764\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190929%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60098050&h=bcd68c25\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190929&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60098050</a>"}]}